                            <comment id="100138" author="olivergierke" created="Tue, 11 Mar 2014 10:26:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We now pipe the id segment obtained from the request URI through Spring HATEOAS&apos; &lt;tt&gt;UriTemplate&lt;/tt&gt; and remove the variables potentially contained in it.&lt;/p&gt;

